          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p dir="ltr">The Like a Dragon--previously called Yakuza--video game series has been around for nearly 20 years, but it's never been more popular in the West than it is today thanks to Yakuza: Like a Dragon and its 2024 sequel Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth. It figures to move even more into the mainstream with the arrival of the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Like-Dragon-Yakuza-Season-Trailer/dp/B0D9PPR5FY?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Like a Dragon: Yakuza TV series</a> on <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/prime/pipeline/signup?tag=gamespot-promos-20&amp;tag=gamespot-buybutton-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Prime Video</a> today, October 24. In honor of the new TV series, several retailers are holding sales on the entire Yakuza series, making now the perfect time to get into the beloved Japanese crime saga. You'll find deals on console and PC versions of the games, including an Amazon discount that drops the most recent game, <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Like-Dragon-Infinite-Wealth-PlayStation-5/dp/B0CJHD3JZ8?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Like A Dragon: Infinite Wealth</a></strong>, to just $30 (normally $70).</p><p dir="ltr">This nearly 60%-off deal is the best price we've seen for Infinite Wealth since its release earlier this year. The discount applies to the PS5, PS4, Xbox (cross-gen) versions of the game, but it's only available for a limited time, so grab it while you can. As mentioned, Infinite Wealth is a direct sequel to Yakuza: Like a Dragon, which starts a new story arc with a brand-new protagonist Ichiban Kasuga. Like a Dragon is a great game to start with if you're new to franchise. Infinite Wealth continues Kasuga's story and brings back Kazuma Kiryu, the original protagonist of the Yakuza series.</p><p dir="ltr">Like a Dragon's PS4 physical edition, which has a free upgrade for PS5 players, is <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08Q6HT9J9?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">only $15 at Amazon</a> and <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fshop-links.co%2F1857376942411315089%3Fu1%3Dsubid_value&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Best Buy</a>. You can also get a cross-generation Xbox physical edition for <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fshop-links.co%2F1857377192262723230%3Fu1%3Dsubid_value&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">$15 at Best Buy</a>, while <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08VXFTPBK?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon</a> has it priced at $20.</p><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Like-Dragon-Infinite-Wealth-PlayStation-5/dp/B0CJHD3JZ8?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth (PS5/PS4/Xbox) at Amazon</a> -- $30 (<del>$70</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08Q6HT9J9?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Yakuza: Like a Dragon (PS4/PS5) at Amazon</a> -- $15</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08VXFTPBK?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Yakuza: Like a Dragon (Series X/Xbox One) at Amazon</a> -- $20</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fshop-links.co%2F1857376942411315089%3Fu1%3Dsubid_value&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Yakuza: Like a Dragon (PS4/PS5 &amp; Xbox) at Best Buy</a> -- $15</li></ul><hr><h2 dir="ltr">Yakuza Franchise Sales - PC</h2><p>For PC players, several online retailers are selling digital versions of Yakuza games for cheap right now:</p><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dpbolvw.net%2Fclick-100770772-15232592%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.gog.com%2Fen%2Fpromo%2F20241024_yakuza_franchise_sale&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">GOG</a></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fhumblebundleinc.sjv.io%2Fc%2F1804712%2F2059850%2F25796%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.humblebundle.com%2Fstore%2Fpromo%2Flike-a-dragon-sale&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Humble Bundle</a></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgreenmangaming.sjv.io%2Fc%2F1804712%2F1219987%2F15105%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenmangaming.com%2Ftitles%2Fyakuza%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Green Man Gaming</a></li></ul><p>Each retailer has slightly different games and discounts on offer, and one of the best deals is <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tkqlhce.com%2Fclick-100770772-15232592%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.gog.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fyakuza_complete_series&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Yakuza Complete Series collection</a></strong> at GOG.</p><h3 dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tkqlhce.com%2Fclick-100770772-15232592%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.gog.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fyakuza_complete_series&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Yakuza Collection at GOG -- Kazuma Kiryu's original 7-game arc for $45</a></h3><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4390185-yakuza.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4390185" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1280" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4390185-yakuza.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4390185"></a><figcaption>Yakuza 6: The Song of Life</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4390185-yakuza.jpg"></figure><p>Despite the collection's title, it only includes seven games: Yakuza Kiwami and Kiwami 2, which are remakes of the first two games, remasters of Yakuza 3-5, Yakuza 6: The Song of Life, and the prequel Yakuza 0. What you're getting here is Kazuma Kiryu's seven-game mainline arc, so it's also a great place to start. Keep in mind that these games are beat-'em-ups, whereas Like a Dragon moved the mainline series in a radically different direction as a turn-based RPG.</p><p>The bundle is 60% off, dropping the price to just $45 (normally $112). While the collection is missing <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jdoqocy.com%2Fclick-100770772-15232592%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.gog.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fyakuza_like_a_dragon&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Yakuza: Like a Dragon</a> and Like a Dragon Infinite Wealth--the seventh and eighth games in the series, respectively--as well as the numerous Yakuza series spin-offs and side games, it's still one of the best--and, currently, most affordable--ways to experience the mainline series from the beginning. Plus, if you buy from GOG, you get DRM-free copies of the games that you can play without the need for third-party launchers like Steam. GOG also has <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jdoqocy.com%2Fclick-100770772-15232592%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.gog.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fyakuza_like_a_dragon&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Yakuza: Like a Dragon on sale for $12</a>.</p><ul><li>Yakuza 0</li><li>Yakuza Kiwami</li><li>Yakuza Kiwami 2</li><li>Yakuza 3 Remastered</li><li>Yakuza 4 Remastered</li><li>Yakuza 5 Remastered</li><li>Yakuza 6: The Song of Life</li></ul><hr><p><strong>More Yakuza Deals at GOG</strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jdoqocy.com%2Fclick-100770772-15232592%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.gog.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fyakuza_like_a_dragon&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Yakuza: Like a Dragon</a> -- $12 (<del>$20</del>)</li><li><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dpbolvw.net%2Fclick-100770772-15232592%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.gog.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fyakuza_series_starter_pack&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Yakuza Kiwami 1 + 2</a> -- $16.49 (<del>$30</del>)</li></ul><hr><h2>Deals on Yakuza Steam Keys</h2><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4390183-ishin.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4390183" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1280" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4390183-ishin.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4390183"></a><figcaption>Like a Dragon: Ishin</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4390183-ishin.jpg"></figure><p dir="ltr">Other PC retailers like Humble Bundle and Green Man Gaming are running similar Yakuza franchise sales, and their discounts include several of the newer games and spin-offs missing from GOG's catalog, including <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgreenmangaming.sjv.io%2Fc%2F1804712%2F1219987%2F15105%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenmangaming.com%2Fgames%2Flike-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-pc%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth</a></strong>, <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgreenmangaming.sjv.io%2Fc%2F1804712%2F1219987%2F15105%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenmangaming.com%2Fgames%2Flike-a-dragon-ishin-pc%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Like a Dragon: Ishin</a></strong>, and <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgreenmangaming.sjv.io%2Fc%2F1804712%2F1219987%2F15105%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenmangaming.com%2Fgames%2Flike-a-dragon-gaiden-the-man-who-erased-his-name-pc%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Like a Dragon Gaiden: The Man Who Erased His Name</a></strong>. There are also price cuts for <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgreenmangaming.sjv.io%2Fc%2F1804712%2F1219987%2F15105%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenmangaming.com%2Fgames%2Fjudgment-pc%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Judgment</a></strong> and <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgreenmangaming.sjv.io%2Fc%2F1804712%2F1219987%2F15105%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenmangaming.com%2Fgames%2Flost-judgment-pc%2F&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="n