PC players can also play the games via Game Pass. Game Pass Ultimate normally costs $20/month, but thanks to <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%2Fclick-100770772-13142092%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Felectronics.woot.com%2Foffers%2Fxbox-game-pass-ultimate-digital-code-1&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">this limited-time deal</a> at the Amazon-owned retailer Woot, you can stock up on prepaid <strong>Game Pass Ultimate codes for as low as $13.79 for the one-month card (normally $20) or $36.49 for the three-month option</strong>.</p><hr><hr><h2 dir="ltr">Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii Preorder Deals</h2><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4390184-pirateyakuza.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4390184" data-ratio="0.56266666666667" data-width="1500" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4390184-pirateyakuza.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4390184"></a><figcaption>Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii Collector's Edition</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1595/15950357/4390184-pirateyakuza.jpg"></figure><p dir="ltr">Speaking of Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii, the upcoming spinoff is available to preorder. Console players can secure physical copies of <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DHLPSVJT?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">the standard</a> or <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DHLP4H7S?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Collector's Edition</a> at Amazon (shown above), but PC players will want to check out <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dpbolvw.net%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Flike-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii-digital-deluxe-edition&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fyakuza-games-are-on-sale-for-cheap-in-celebration-of-new-prime-video-series%2F1100-6527384%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Fanatical's preorder deal</a></strong> for the Steam version, which drops the price to $53 for the standard edition (normally $60) or $66 for the Digital Deluxe Edition (normally $75).</p><hr><p dir="ltr">Lastly, if you're looking for Like a Dragon merch, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/53155B57-7024-4891-8CBD-E7EEE1E9A85D?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon launched a new merch page</a> in honor of the Like a Dragon: Yakuza Prime Video series that features apparel, phone cases, and tumblers with designs inspired by the video games.</p><p dir="ltr"><em>Disclosure: GameSpot and Fanatical are both owned by Fandom</em></p><hr><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/elden-ring-official-art-books-are-b1g1-50-off-at-amazon-get-both-for-only-59/1100-6527378/">Elden Ring Official Art Books Are B1G1 50% Off At Amazon - Get Both For Only $59</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/horror-movie-tv-series-box-set-collection-amazon-halloween-deals/1100-6527353/">Best Horror Movie 4K Box Sets And Steelbook Deals At Amazon Ahead Of Halloween</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/dune-limited-time-amazon-deals-all-6-dune-books-for-38-4k-box-set-for-lowest-price-yet/1100-6527343/">Dune Limited-Time Amazon Deals - All 6 Dune Books For $38, 4K Box Set For Lowest Price Yet</a></li>                          <